description: Demolition of existing buildings and erection of part 4 rising to part 9 storey building for use as a health and wellbeing centre on the ground and first floors plus a retail (Class A1/A3) unit on the ground floor together with 34 x 1 bedroom flats and 49 x 2 bedroom flats (total 83 flats) on the upper floors with ramp to basement and 46 basement car parking spaces (including 4 disabled spaces) together with refuse and recycling facilities, cycle storage and landscaping proposals
